content.text:
State update bug found. `addItem` mutates the original state object by using `const next = state` instead of creating a copy.

Fix in `useCartState.mjs`:
```javascript
export function addItem(state, item) {
  const next = { ...state, items: [...state.items], total: state.items.length + 1 }
  next.items.push(item)
  return next
}
```

